data.description: 2.75% assumable Loan. Seller will consider an offer reflecting assuming the VA loan currently on the property. Tucked back in a cul-de-sac this home has great shade trees and a spacious yard. The kitchen is dreamy with plenty of counter space, cabinet storage, and giant island. The primary suite has a jetted tub-shower combination. The dining room, kitchen and living room are open concept with epoxy flooring in the living room. This home is close to Dyess AFB, Clack MS and many other amenities. Make it yours today!
